npcs.name: Joshua
npcs.message:
Hey! I'm Joshua! I'm a technical leader and polyglot full-stack developer with 25+ years of experience. I've delivered over 200 technical projects for large and small businesses alike and I have helped over a dozen startups develop and ship their ideas. I've talked on and hosted podcasts about building software and shared my perspective on growing as a developer through public speaking, working with university courses and mentoring developer cohorts. I love growing people, but I'm still an engineer at heart. 

I don't suppose you could give me a hand. I seem to have lost my badge to get into work.

If you could find it, that'd be awesome!
